creator: Ella Wheeler Wilcox
description:
LibriVox recording of Poems of Purpose by Ella Wheeler Wilcox.
Read in English by Ken Masters; Ian King; Rosslyn Carlyle; Carol; MaryAnn; Julia Niedermaier; Shakira Searle; Soumen Barua; Rani K.
This is a volume of poems by Ella Wheeler Wilcox, published in 1919. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

Download M4B (51MB)
